OL,3,CWindrush scandal: Compensation scheme
OL,4,Cbranded 'a failure' amid calls for
OL,5,Creform
OL,7,FThe Government's compensation scheme
OL,8,Ffor victims of the Windrush scandal
OL,9,Fhas been branded a failure as
OL,10,Fcampaigners urged ministers to
OL,11,Foverhaul the payout process five years
OL,12,Fsince it was launched.
OL,14,FCritics of the beleaguered scheme have
OL,15,Frepeatedly called for the Home Office
OL,16,Fto be stripped of responsibility for
OL,17,Fdetermining and handling payments to
OL,18,Fvictims and said it should be turned
OL,19,Fover to an independent body instead.
