OL,7,FDespite growing concerns around the
OL,8,Fnumber of people dying before
OL,9,Freceiving payouts, the Home Office has
OL,10,Fso far resisted demands for such
OL,11,Freforms, warning that changing how the
OL,12,Fsystem is administered could disrupt
OL,13,Fclaims being processed and lead to
OL,14,Fdelayed payments.
