OL,3,CWindrush scandal: Compensation scheme
OL,4,Cbranded 'a failure' amid calls for
OL,5,Creform
OL,7,FConroy Downie, a 67-year-old Windrush
OL,8,Fvictim who has been advising thousands
OL,9,Fof others on how to make compensation
OL,10,Fclaims and is still waiting for his
OL,11,Fcase to be fully settled, told the PA
OL,12,Fnews agency: "It's a failure, it's
OL,13,Fdisgusting. I think they are waiting
OL,14,Ffor us to die off."
