OL,7,FWhile there have been "some
OL,8,Fimprovements" over the years, "we are
OL,9,Fstill some way to go to say the scheme
OL,10,Fis operating in an efficient way", she
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FCaroline Abrahams, charity director at
OL,14,FAge UK, said while the latest figures
OL,15,Fshow "modest improvements" in the
OL,16,Fperformance of the scheme, "many
OL,17,Fpeople are still waiting far too long
OL,18,Ffor the redress they are due ` over a
OL,19,Fyear or even 18 months in the worst
OL,20,Fcases".
