OL,7,FShe added: "This is unacceptable,
OL,8,Fespecially given that for many of the
OL,9,Folder applicants time is not on their
OL,10,Fside."
OL,12,FRepeating calls to "shift the scheme's
OL,13,Fadministration to an independent body,
OL,14,Fso claimants have the confidence to
OL,15,Fapply" and for a "redesign" so it
OL,16,Fprovides "fair recompense" for loss of
OL,17,Ffuture earnings and pensions income,
OL,18,FMs Abrahams said: "The Windrush
OL,19,Fcompensation scheme can be made fairer
OL,20,Fand easier to access if the political
OL,21,Fwill is there in Government.
