OL,7,F"It's high time everyone affected
OL,8,Freceived the justice they are due
OL,9,Fbefore it's too late and more people
OL,10,Fgo to their graves uncompensated for
OL,11,Fthe enormous harm they and their
OL,12,Ffamilies have experienced through the
OL,13,Fyears."
OL,15,FThe comments follow calls last month
OL,16,Fin the Lords for Windrush scandal
OL,17,Fvictims to have similar support to
OL,18,Fthose affected by the Post Office
OL,19,Fscandal.
