OL,7,FSome 4,847 claims had been fully
OL,8,Fclosed by this time, of which just
OL,9,Fover half (52%) were found to have no
OL,10,Fentitlement to compensation, 36% were
OL,11,Foffered compensation, and the
OL,12,Fremaining 12% had their eligibility
OL,13,Ffor a claim refused or withdrawn.
OL,15,FOf the 1,345 claims still being
OL,16,Fprocessed, 185 (14%) had been in the
OL,17,Fsystem for at least 12 months,
OL,18,Fincluding 83 for more than 18 months.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/15
