OL,7,FThis is a slight improvement on a year
OL,8,Fago; at the end of January 2023, 19%
OL,9,Fof claims (416 out of 2,192) had been
OL,10,Fin the system for a year or more, with
OL,11,F171 for more than 18 months.
OL,13,FThe 12 month-plus proportion has crept
OL,14,Fupwards in recent months, however,
OL,15,Fhaving dipped as low as 12% in October
OL,16,F2023. It peaked at 38% in June 2022.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/15
