OL,7,F"We firmly believe moving the
OL,8,Foperation of the scheme away from the
OL,9,FHome Office would risk significantly
OL,10,Fdelaying vital payments to people `
OL,11,Fthere would be considerable disruption
OL,12,Fto the processing of outstanding
OL,13,Fclaims whilst a new body was
OL,14,Festablished and made operational," a
OL,15,Fspokeswoman added.
OL,17,FA candlelit vigil and rally is set to
OL,18,Ftake place in Brixton, south London,
OL,19,Fon Saturday to mark the sixth
OL,20,Fanniversary since the scandal was
OL,21,Fexposed.
